<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 21:10:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Brembo“见机行事”，2024 年销量预测谨慎</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/brembo-plays-it-by-ear-with-cagey-2024-sales-forecast-2024-03-05/</link><description>意大利布雷博 (Brembo) 周二发表了谨慎的展望，预计今年收入将实现中个位数增长，与 2023 年的业绩一致，因为地缘政治和商业紧张局势使未来业务前景的可见度有限。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 17:18:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/brembo-plays-it-by-ear-with-cagey-2024-sales-forecast-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>立法者寻求迫使字节跳动剥离 TikTok，否则将面临美国禁令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/lawmakers-seek-force-bytedance-divest-tiktok-or-face-us-ban-2024-03-05/</link><description>美国两党议员小组周二提出立法，将给中国字节跳动大约六个月的时间剥离流行的短视频应用 TikTok，否则将面临美国禁令。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 17:14:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/lawmakers-seek-force-bytedance-divest-tiktok-or-face-us-ban-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，在市场紧张的情况下，全球房价将温和攀升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/poll-global-home-prices-set-gentle-climb-tight-market-2024-03-05/</link><description>路透社对住房专家的调查显示，今年和明年大多数主要房地产市场的房价将小幅上涨，他们预计经济适用房短缺的情况将至少持续两到三年。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 13:30:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/poll-global-home-prices-set-gentle-climb-tight-market-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯称正在考虑与中国合作在月球上建设核电站</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/russia-china-are-considering-putting-nuclear-power-unit-moon-ria-2024-03-05/</link><description>俄罗斯航天局局长尤里·鲍里索夫周二表示，俄罗斯和中国正在考虑从 2033 年至 35 年在月球上建造一座核电站，他表示，有一天可能会允许在月球上建造定居点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 12:28:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/russia-china-are-considering-putting-nuclear-power-unit-moon-ria-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>据英国《金融时报》报道，新加坡淡马锡正在洽谈投资 OpenAI</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/singapores-temasek-talks-invest-openai-ft-reports-2024-03-05/</link><description>英国《金融时报》周二援引两位知情人士的话报道称，新加坡淡马锡控股公司正在讨论投资微软支持的人工智能公司 OpenAI。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 12:13:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/singapores-temasek-talks-invest-openai-ft-reports-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：苹果焦虑、特斯拉坦克、比特币犹豫</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-05/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 11:11:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>法国“蜘蛛侠”攀登塔楼支持菲律宾南海主张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/french-spiderman-scales-tower-support-philippines-south-china-sea-claims-2024-03-05/</link><description>周二，一名被称为“法国蜘蛛侠”的自由攀登者爬上了马尼拉的一座摩天大楼，以支持菲律宾在有争议的南中国海的海洋主张。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 10:36:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/french-spiderman-scales-tower-support-philippines-south-china-sea-claims-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>葡萄牙建筑商 Mota-Engil 2023 年利润增长一倍多</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/portuguese-builder-mota-engil-more-than-doubles-2023-profit-2024-03-05/</link><description>葡萄牙最大的建筑商周二表示，由于销售额创历史新高，Mota-Engil 2023 年净利润增长了一倍多，而需求将其订单量推升至前所未有的 130 亿欧元（141 亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 09:36:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/portuguese-builder-mota-engil-more-than-doubles-2023-profit-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>独家：碧桂园贷款人集团聘请顾问进行债务重组谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/country-garden-lenders-group-hires-advisers-debt-revamp-talks-sources-say-2024-03-05/</link><description>三位知情人士称，中国碧桂园的一组贷款人已聘请安理国际会计师事务所(Allen &amp;amp; Overy)和德勤(Deloitte)作为顾问，而这家陷入困境的开发商的债权人正在为可能的债务重组谈判做好准备。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 09:24:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/country-garden-lenders-group-hires-advisers-debt-revamp-talks-sources-say-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>台湾敦促与中国进行无政治先决条件的对话</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-urges-dialogue-with-china-without-political-preconditions-2024-03-05/</link><description>北京在一份政府工作报告中强化了在台湾问题上的立场后，台湾陆委会周二敦促中国接受两岸互不隶属的事实。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 08:46:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-urges-dialogue-with-china-without-political-preconditions-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国改革不力，欧洲股市下跌；科技导致亏损</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-fall-over-underwhelming-chinese-stimulus-data-tap-2024-03-05/</link><description>欧洲主要股指周二下跌，因最大消费国中国缺乏实质性刺激措施，矿业股随金属价格走软，而投资者等待本周欧元区和美国经济数据以及欧洲央行政策决定。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 08:16:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-fall-over-underwhelming-chinese-stimulus-data-tap-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>沃尔沃汽车 2 月份销量下滑 2%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-february-sales-volume-down-2-year-on-year-2024-03-05/</link><description>总部位于瑞典的沃尔沃汽车公司周二表示，2月份销量同比下降2%至50,315辆，并指出中国农历新年是销量下降的主要原因。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 08:06:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-february-sales-volume-down-2-year-on-year-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>德国舍弗勒2023年核心利润未达预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/germanys-schaeffler-misses-expectations-2023-core-profit-2024-03-05/</link><description>德国汽车和工业供应商舍弗勒股份公司周二公布的2023年全年调整后核心利润（EBIT）为11.9亿欧元（12.9亿美元），受到中国对该集团工业部门需求疲软的拖累。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 08:05:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/germanys-schaeffler-misses-expectations-2023-core-profit-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾、美国将在面向南海和台湾的岛屿举行军事演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-hold-military-drills-islands-facing-south-china-sea-taiwan-2024-03-05/</link><description>随着该地区与中国的紧张局势持续发酵，菲律宾和美国将于下个月在菲律宾面临南海的岛屿和台湾等关键地点举行年度军事演习。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 07:49:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-hold-military-drills-islands-facing-south-china-sea-taiwan-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>由于财政火箭弹难以捉摸，中国投资者坚持逢低买入</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/investors-china-stick-bargains-fiscal-bazooka-proves-elusive-2024-03-05/</link><description>重返中国复苏股市的外国投资者表示，周二宣布的支出计划不足以扭转低迷的情绪，目前继续买入股票的主要原因是股价便宜。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 07:20:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/investors-china-stick-bargains-fiscal-bazooka-proves-elusive-2024-03-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>